Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.54,0:01:30.96,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)\pos(320,348)}即便一切 天翻地覆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.56,0:01:33.02,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)\pos(320,348)}唯有那件 唯有那件
